# Population Density Integration Specification
## FEMA NextGen Emergency Coordination Platform

**Document ID:** ARCH-POP-001  
**Classification:** UNCLASSIFIED // FOUO  
**Date:** 2024-11-14  
**Author:** Senior Technical Architect, Meridian Systems

---

## 1. Integration Overview

### 1.1 Purpose
Integrate aggregated cell-tower density data into the dispatch optimization engine to provide real-time population visibility for ambulance routing and shelter demand estimation.

### 1.2 Scope
- **In Scope:** Aggregated population density at census block group resolution (minimum 100 individuals per unit)
- **Out of Scope:** Individual device tracking, historical pattern analysis beyond 72 hours, predictive modeling

### 1.3 Data Source
Commercial aggregated mobility data provider (carrier-derived, de-identified, compliant with FCC Docket 15-144 framework for emergency response use).

---

