## 3. API Contracts

### 3.1 Population Density Query API

**Endpoint:** `GET /api/v1/population-density/query`

**Request Parameters:**
| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |
|-----------|------|----------|-------------|
| `bbox` | string | yes | Bounding box as `lat1,lon1,lat2,lon2` |
| `timestamp` | ISO8601 | no | Defaults to latest available |
| `resolution` | enum | no | `block_group` (default), `tract`, `county` |
| `include_baseline` | boolean | no | Include census baseline for comparison |

**Response:**
```json
{
  "query_result": {
    "timestamp": "2024-11-14T14:30:00Z",
    "bbox": [27.8, -82.8, 28.0, -82.5],
    "resolution": "block_group",
    "features": [
      {
        "geoid": "120950001002",
        "geometry": { "type": "Polygon", "coordinates": [...] },
        "properties": {
          "current_population": 1247,
          "baseline_population": 3421,
          "deviation_percent": -63.5,
          "confidence": 0.94
        }
      }
    ],
    "summary": {
      "total_current": 45821,
      "total_baseline": 127400,
      "area_evacuation_rate": 0.64
    }
  },
  "metadata": {
    "data_freshness_seconds": 180,
    "provider": "aggregated_mobility_v2",
    "coverage_completeness": 0.97
  }
}
```

### 3.2 Dispatch Optimization Integration

**Endpoint:** `POST /api/v1/dispatch/optimize`

**Extended Request Body:**
```json
{
  "incident_id": "INC-2024-1114-0847",
  "incident_location": { "lat": 27.8921, "lon": -82.6844 },
  "resource_pool": ["AMB-FL-04-0142", "AMB-FL-04-0143", "AMB-FL-04-0148"],
  "optimization_parameters": {
    "objective": "minimize_response_time",
    "population_weighting": {
      "enabled": true,
      "density_feed": "realtime",
      "weight_factor": 0.3,
      "rationale": "prioritize_routes through populated areas during evacuation"
    }
  },
  "constraints": {
    "avoid_zero_population_zones": true,
    "shelter_demand_mode": false
  }
}
```

